<item>
            <title>[LUCENE-2847] Support all of unicode in StandardTokenizer</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LUCENE-2847</link>
                <project id="12310110" key="LUCENE">Lucene - Core</project>
                        <description>&lt;p&gt;StandardTokenizer currently only supports the BMP.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;If it encounters characters outside of the BMP, it just discards them... &lt;br/&gt;
it should instead implement fully implement UAX#29 across all of unicode.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
            <key id="12494750">LUCENE-2847</key>
            <summary>Support all of unicode in StandardTokenizer</summary>
